    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved and maintained over the years. It still looks great and drives even better\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable, comfy car for their daily commute or weekend getaways! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for it to find a great new owner. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
